<div class="row">
    <div class="col-5 text-center my-auto">
        <img class="border border-1" width=100% src="/assets/img/drowsydriving.png" />
    </div>
    <div class="col-6 text-center">
        <div class="timeline-panel pl-1">
            <div class="timeline-heading pl-2">
                <h3>Predicted Crash Severity : @ViewBag.drowsy_driving</h3>
                <h6 class="subheading">
                    @if (ViewBag.seatbelt == "1")
                    {<p>Minor accident with no injuries</p>}
                    else if (ViewBag.seatbelt == "2")
                    {<p>Minor accident with possible injuries</p>}
                    else if (ViewBag.seatbelt == "3")
                    {<p>Accident with minor injuries</p>}
                    else if (ViewBag.seatbelt == "4")
                    {<p>Accident with serious injuries</p>}
                    else
                    {<p>Major accident with one or more fatalities</p>}
                </h6>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-body"><p class="text-muted"><a href="https://www.nsc.org/road-safety/safety-topics/fatigued-driving#:~:text=The%20National%20Highway%20Traffic%20Safety,the%20time%20of%20a%20crash.">The National Highway Traffic Safety Administration</a> estimates that every year about 100,000 police-reported, drowsy-driving crashes result in nearly 800 fatalities and about 50,000 injuries. <br /><br />Be cautious when driving for long periods of time or late at night. Don't put yourself or others at risk.</p></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<br />
